Title: The Walk
Plot: After a suicide attempt and multiple murders at a military hospital, Mulder and Scully meet a quadruple amputee who has gained the power of astral projection and is taking out his personal frustrations on his commanding officers.
GuestStars: Thomas Kopache, Willie Garson, Paula Shaw, Deryl Hayes, Rob Lee, Andrea Barclay, Beatrice Zeilinger, Brennan Kotowich, Pat Bermel, Paul Dickson, D. Harlan Cutshall, Don Thompson, Nancy Sorel, Ian Tracey
